<plot>Haunted by childhood memories of his father's murder, Frank Carroll, private detective/circus clown, sets out on a mission of vengeance. Jingles Carroll, a gentle man in a red nose, was gunned down in cold blood by Max &amp; Fudge, two members of a secret society, as his young son watched in horror. Now, twenty years later, Frank strikes back.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?008686</url></doc>
